div.font: Edge Adapters source events, convert them into CloudEvents and publish them to Kafka. FX provides support for many sources out of the box. Additional sources can be added by adding a suitable Edge Adapter.

div.font: Consumes CloudEvents, enriches them with technical data and publishes them for consumption by the Executors. It keeps a track of the Executions and maintains service flow.

div.font: Clusters of Executors run services based on the mapping of EventTypes to Services. Services emit events which may be consumed by other services to create service flows. Executors pull service code from GIT.
